# FB:Messenger UPDATE - the "Nicolas Cage" Reaction
Because you deserve it.


![N|Solid]( data:image/png;base64,)

It is a chrome extension allowing to react to Facebook messages with Nicolas Cage. Because it was missing.

# Installation
Push the extention on the store was too complicated, I propose you install it by yourself ! :
  - Clone this repo
  - In chrome, go to  : chrome://extensions/
  - Enable the Developper Mode if you have to, and click "Load unpackaged extension"
  - Select the right folder
